#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1567
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "These running totals help you spot operations you may have forgotten to "
#| "enter in &skrooge;. Many bank statements provide similar totals such as "
#| "\"Withdrawals\" or \"Deposits and Credits\", although they may have "
#| "separate totals for \"Interest\", \"Fees\". When the Delta is equal to 0, "
#| "you <emphasis>may</emphasis> have pointed all operations matching the "
#| "bank's record. For example, you may have mistakenly pointed a debit of 8€ "
#| "and a credit of 2€, and overlooked a bank debit of 6€ - the net is the "
#| "same, minus 6€. When the Delta is 0, the <guibutton>Validate pointed "
#| "operations button <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
#| "\"validate.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
#| "guibutton> is enabled. Click on this button to complete your "
#| "reconciliation: all pointed operations are now checked."
msgid ""
"These running totals help you spot transactions you may have forgotten to "
"enter in &skrooge;. Many bank statements provide similar totals such as "
"\"Withdrawals\" or \"Deposits and Credits\", although they may have separate "
"totals for \"Interest\", \"Fees\". When the Delta is equal to 0, you "
"<emphasis>may</emphasis> have marked all transactions matching the bank's "
"record. For example, you may have mistakenly marked a debit of 8€ and a "
"credit of 2€, and overlooked a bank debit of 6€ - the net is the same, minus "
"6€. When the Delta is 0, the <guibutton>Validate marked transactions button "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"validate.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> is enabled. Click on "
"this button to complete your reconciliation: all marked transactions are now "
"checked."
msgstr ""
"Isto ajuda-o a detectar operações que se possa ter esquecido de introduzir "
"no &skrooge;. Muitos extractos bancários oferecem valores totais semelhantes "
"do tipo \"Levantamentos\" ou \"Depósitos e Créditos\", ainda que possam ter "
"totais separados para \"Juros\" e \"Taxas\". Quando o Delta for igual a 0, "
"<emphasis>poderá</emphasis> já ter apontado como verificadas todas as "
"operações que correspondem aos registos bancários. Por exemplo, poderá ter "
"apontar por engano um débito de 8€ e um crédito de 2€, tendo ignorado um "
"débito bancário de 6€; o valor líquido é o mesmo, menos 6€. Quando o Delta "
"for 0, o botão para <guibutton>Validar as operações apontadas "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"validate.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> fica activo. "
"Carregue neste botão para terminar a sua reconciliação: todas as operações "
"apontadas estão agora verificadas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1569
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "can automatically point all imported operations for you."
msgid "can automatically mark all imported transactions for you."
msgstr "poderá apontar automaticamente todas as operações importadas para si."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1571
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the option <guibutton>Hide checked operations</guibutton> for the "
#| "table is selected from its \"Show\" menu (see <link linkend=\"show"
