#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you no longer need the tracker, for example, because it has been fully "
"reimbursed, you may simply delete it. Doing, this, however, will discard all "
"information you have entered, which you may not wish to do as such "
"information may be of use to you in the future."
